==============================================================================
Name: Deathmatch Hivac 
==============================================================================
Gamemode: Deathmatch
Release Date: 
Version: RC 1
Author: Prototstar
Homepage http://www.prototstar.com
==============================================================================
Description: Hivac a medium size map suitable for an intense 12 players DEATHMATCH.
==============================================================================
Instruction: 

1. Extract it to your Counter Strike Source/cstrike/maps folder.
2. Start up Counter Strike Source.
3. Start server and select map.
4. Play!
